Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,咆哮吧 呼吼吧 終極絕招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.30,0:01:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.40,0:01:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.40,0:01:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明打中了卻沒有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那攻擊是從哪個方向來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.20,0:02:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙 兩面加擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就盡情享受這死亡的旋律吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.70,0:02:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一對一不是正好嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.27,0:02:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說呢 左近
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四人眾也未免太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:14.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道碰到了讓他們都頭疼的對手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說玩得太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拖後腿的總是肚子一直餓的次郎坊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.13,0:03:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有貪玩的鬼童丸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.80,0:03:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過一旦發飆 最麻煩的人就是左近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不把敵人殺死絕不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明放走就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.50,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,硬要證明自己是四人眾最強的一個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多由也也是從來都不肯認輸的臭脾氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正不管如何 他去就萬無一失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君麻呂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會將我眼前那些無用的垃圾掃除乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決不會把佐助交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.10,0:04:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾散落了一地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.40,0:04:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過垃圾畢竟只是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要簡單清掃一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.30,0:04:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.20,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打垮你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.20,0:05:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的死亡旋律嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用笛聲操縱它們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.20,0:06:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 離那傢伙越來越遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.90,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回真的糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊才是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.00,0:06:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多連拳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再接一招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.60,0:06:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是很親密的兄弟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時哥哥右近在我的體內沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.00,0:06:50.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥時就會出來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.60,0:06:53.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是他的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.00,0:06:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右近可以從我身體內的任何一個部位
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伸出頭來幫我防禦或者進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.70,0:07:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多連腳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 三隻腳一起踢 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,效果不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.60,0:07:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左近 沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速戰速決 進入狀態二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥還真是心急
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來那個角並不是什麼裝飾品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右邊的傢伙出現後
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的查克拉提升了數十倍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來就夠糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還雪上加霜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥喜歡怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎屍萬段
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該認真點了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣收拾你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是蠻能說的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這句話該我說才對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個糾纏不休的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.35,0:09:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我已經看出點端倪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過 問題才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 到此為止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:30.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 用那個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡沒同伴接應 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.35,0:09:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.25,0:09:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那招忍術的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我都會耗盡查克拉 無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒打中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就必死無疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.15,0:09:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然被你咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真是個沒用的主人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.95,0:10:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.95,0:10:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的對
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有用那招了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.85,0:10:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙狼牙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.95,0:10:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好幹啊 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他看看我們的修煉成果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.55,0:10:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中動態追蹤
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用這種骯髒的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬塚流.人獸混合變身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:09.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙頭狼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為是什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.85,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是口水滴滴答答的小狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種傢伙能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是口水
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.65,0:11:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左近 你搞什麼 右邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙狼牙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.35,0:12:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 牙狼牙的迴旋速度很快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是令我們的視線都能變為零的超速旋轉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.55,0:12:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不直接接觸 也能斬斷身體
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.15,0:12:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正中的話就四分五裂了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.05,0:12:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 囂張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好 我正準備一分為二呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.35,0:12:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分成兩個人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.65,0:12:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單一個體被擊中就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.15,0:12:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戲才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.55,0:13:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.75,0:13:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙狼牙還有一發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.15,0:13:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是極限了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.75,0:13:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣解決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙狼牙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲起來也沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過我們不是靠眼睛追蹤的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.75,0:13:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是追著標記留下的氣味攻擊的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術.羅生門
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.45,0:14:01.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是驚人的威力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把保護大蛇丸大人的最強防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅生門撞成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.55,0:14:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:29.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸 你為了保護我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.95,0:14:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一次不是普通的小便
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼球好像被強酸灼傷了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.55,0:14:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.83,0:14:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面就交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.74,0:14:59.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就到那條河裡去洗洗眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.45,0:15:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗殺專家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.45,0:15:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單靠鋒利的爪子\N和敏銳的嗅覺是贏不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我有這種能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.75,0:15:20.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道流動著查克拉的經絡系統
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.29,0:15:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纏繞著各個內臟器官
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.95,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經絡系統
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅僅連著構成各個器官的組織
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就連構成組織的細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至組成這些細胞的主要成分蛋白質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也複雜多樣地連接著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態二的我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠自由利用查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.01,0:15:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重新分解構成細胞或蛋白質
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.15,0:15:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡單來說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以將自己的身體分解潛入敵人的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.25,0:15:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後恢復成原樣脫離出來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.15,0:16:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直與你走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何時何地都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是好孩子 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掉進陷阱的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.75,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛好帶著我們需要的地之書
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.55,0:16:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們是第一了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸突然開始害怕起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸能嗅出敵人的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.55,0:16:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並判斷其強弱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此害怕 還是頭一回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.35,0:16:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前邊交手的那些傢伙決不是泛泛之輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第七回合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.15,0:16:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漩渦鳴人對犬塚牙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:01.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你怎麼帶著小狗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.25,0:17:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會妨礙比賽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 赤丸也要一起上的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.55,0:17:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.85,0:17:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中計了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把赤丸還過來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你給它吃什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛的顏色突然變紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才叫它赤丸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:01.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擬獸忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獸人分身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.05,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.35,0:18:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四腳之術
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破綻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招 獸人體術奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.95,0:19:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.35,0:19:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是兵糧丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤丸 擬人忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牙通牙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 這一次只能認輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的細胞在你體內自由地來回游動
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.25,0:20:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以製造出專屬你的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.05,0:20:14.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們正處於融合狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.95,0:20:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共享這個肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,共享
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.95,0:20:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.25,0:20:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有惟獨我能做到的殘忍殺人手法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.35,0:20:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢奪走屬於你的細胞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.15,0:20:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然自殺 這怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同歸於盡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.65,0:22:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.75,0:22:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是血繼限界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.35,0:22:45.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種招式簡直前所未見
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.95,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以如此龐大的數量衝了上去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.35,0:22:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然奈何不了他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.85,0:22:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管你有哪五種舞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會徹底解決你的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.65,0:23:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.49,0:23:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各自的戰鬥
